the same is true of dorff , who gets a thankless role despite actually having some talent ( something that has happened to him a lot ) .
reid is pretty much exactly what she should be , background sex appeal , as whenever she tries to act it is a disaster ( as is the incredibly bad scientist look she has in the beginning).in
