if they keep ruining the spirit like this , it 's only a matter of time before samus aran is killing middle - easterns with an ak-47 and
tommy vercetti is fighting a squadron of aliens .
unlike resident evil , however , this one does n't deserve a second chance , as i do n't think anything could possibly help me forget just how terrible this movie is .
