it is the story of a awkward , yet loving daughter ( leigh ) , devoted to her father ( finney ) after her mother dies during childbirth .
the arrogant father holds his daughter in no esteem whatsoever , and considers her , as well as all women , simpleminded .
when a young man ( chaplin ) of good family and little fortune comes courting , the father is naturally suspicious , but feeling so sure that his daughter could hold no interest for any man , is convinced that the young man is a fortune hunter and forbids her to see him .
