a kind of symbolic rape , the girl runs away , both aroused and repelled by this man 's interest .
but de niro 's performance , so deliciously over the top , simply ca n't be imitated by scorsese .
you 'd need the operatic tone and the baroque visuals of someone like de palma to make this work .
