what we do is this : we have the dalai lama befriend the now - reformed nazi because the latter is so good at fiddling with film projectors , radios , antique cars , and any other devices with represent the freedom of the capitalist west .
in return , our hero learns from his young protegé a kind of vague , undefined buddhism which is never really brought out or treated in a serious fashion .
