then it was time to stop messing around .
i walked back into the first theater , found my seat , and looked up to see that the impending lois lane space shuttle disaster was almost upon us .
still , it seemed to be taking forever , so i wandered around the theater , met a girl , got married , raised a son and sent him off to college .
