a wimpy orlando bloom type called ilias , from some society vaguely resembling ancient greece travels across the ocean to caveman territory on some vaguely defined quest to battle evil , where he joins up with a animal loving hunter to battle the wolf - man and mutant minions of a vampiric topless evil sorceress .
